<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Agree with you on that. How did a spy become an architect? Well, the trick of it is we have Henry Cort and then we have William Cort; but when charact<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Agree with you on that. How did a spy become an architect? Well, the trick of it is we have Henry Cort and then we have William Cort; but when characters are largely referred to by only their last name, knowing which is which isn't very clear.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
